title: Fox Adventure v1.1.0
description:
*** This game is puzzle. ***
*** Test your brain. Try challenge if you're smart!! ***

Hora starts dangerous journey to rescue his grandfather. episode 1

- 51 stages
- 6 useful items
- various floors and traps
- 3 bonus items in a stage
- Korean, English support

Use items you can get in each stage, you'll clear the stages easily.
the puzzle is not difficult. but the stages with traps and puzzles may frustrate you.
however, you'll overcome.

You may praise yourself when you finish this game.

What's New:

- user interface changed.
- display difficulty
- some graphics changed.
- some stage difficulty is down
- bug fix

More info:
 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.day4shine.FoxAdventure
